      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i dont really want to bother the surgeon for something small like this, they're super busy and i'm sure it's just healing. if i just do the warm compress a few times a day and keep the ointment on it, it should clear up on its own right? like it's only a tiny bit of yellow stuff, not like a huge amount.",
